{"tid":1573410,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"岳義士被送往東區醫院，目前在腦科病房留醫，情況穩定。","createTime":"2019-09-16T03:46:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-16T15:53:43.000Z","uid":68738,"like":52,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"7d09da1b55f3014333456246099e1b9b274cf6fb","tid":1573410,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T03:46:49.000Z","msg":"大批市民昨日（15日）各自到港島「行街」後，警方展開清場行動，在多區拘捕市民，晚上北角、炮台山一帶亦發生多宗打鬥事件。其中在七海商業中心附近，一名灰衫青年為救被制服的男子，遂從後襲擊一名防暴警察。灰衫青年被多名警員制服後，遭警棍打至血流披面，警員甚至向他迎面施胡椒噴霧。青年其後被送往東區醫院救治，目前情況穩定，有律師已跟進其個案。<br />\n<br />\n事發時，一批防暴警察在七海商業中心附近的停車場追捕多名男子，其間有3人被制服，蹲在地上，一名年約20歲、身穿灰色上衣、沒有戴口罩的青年拿出一支棍狀物，從後襲擊一名防暴警察，被制服人士隨即逃去。<br />\n<br />\n灰衫青年亦轉身跑離現場，但被多名警員追捕。青年其後跌倒，隨即遭警員撳在地上，又箍頸制服。青年掙扎期間，警員喝止「唔好反抗」，一邊用警棍打他的手，一邊稱「否則使用武力」，隨後甚至將青年撻在地上。青年被打爆頭浴血，雙手被綁在背後，其間青年沒有反抗，但仍遭警員用胡椒噴劑噴面。<span style=\"color: red;\">青年最後被送往東區醫院，目前在腦科病房留醫，情況穩定。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190916/60049439?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190916%2F60049439%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=qpM4horlrIen4ao1f4l1xUYD92OErucUe%2F0sHRi%2FZkY%3D&h=e7210eef\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190916%2F60049439%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=5222ec65\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190916/60049439?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a>"},{"pid":"4505730c43c48f1f133faffb26a18ce97bb7581a","tid":1573410,"uid":199007,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T03:48:56.000Z","msg":"一定要無事!"},{"pid":"f9ecf8a73f7a82fb595c0578f6ab1be330a3a20d","tid":1573410,"uid":54264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T03:49:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecb5c383895d975f9216789f1fe2560d22df752b","tid":1573410,"uid":44930,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T03:53:36.000Z","msg":"一定要平安，要錢醫要出聲，一定要用最好嘅腦科醫生"},{"pid":"0f18d458ca966deb84b92e05fdd92f4100251645","tid":1573410,"uid":248290,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T03:57:46.000Z","msg":"義士 <br />\n打狗 救人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc6d380e1e2ba35b77f89bd6adef73ef043fbbd5","tid":1573410,"uid":61766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T04:18:46.000Z","msg":"借個位<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你地開心啦，尋晚中秋前線小朋友食得一個包咋<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1567456\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1567456</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"dbfa28e26346928416bb5e1931f53455fe0b067b","tid":1573410,"uid":290314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T04:22:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c2f67d764c609f85235d071a9d75ab38a8742a50","tid":1573410,"uid":229886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T04:34:13.000Z","msg":"屋企人有冇事？<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cdc04557c5b908b6cd41d7316c2858fa017d759","tid":1573410,"uid":282777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"r